text: Two of my three brothers are Republicans, but there are core things we are fighting for together. People across the country are ready for an America that works for everyone. 2020 is our moment is history. I know what’s broken, and I know how to fix it. #DemDebate

text: The @CFPB was an example of dreaming big and fighting hard. People told me, go for something little. Go for something that the big corporations will be able to accept. I said no. Let's go for an agency that will make big, structural change in our economy. #DemDebate
text_html: The @CFPB was an example of dreaming big and fighting hard. People told me, go for something little. Go for something that the big corporations will be able to accept. I said no. Let's go for an agency that will make big, structural change in our economy. #DemDebate

text: After the financial crisis, I had an idea for a consumer agency that would stop banks from cheating people. Republicans, big banks, even Democrats told me: You’ll never get it passed. But I fought hard. To date, the @CFPB has returned $12 billion to American consumers. #DemDebate
text_html: After the financial crisis, I had an idea for a consumer agency that would stop banks from cheating people. Republicans, big banks, even Democrats told me: You’ll never get it passed. But I fought hard. To date, the @CFPB has returned $12 billion to American consumers. #DemDebate

text: We need to address the elephant in the room: How campaigns are financed. Today, I announced that I’m not taking any money from Big Pharma, Big Tech, or Wall Street executives. You can’t go behind closed doors, take their money and then expect them to enforce the rules. #DemDebate
text_html: We need to address the elephant in the room: How campaigns are financed. Today, I announced that I’m not taking any money from Big Pharma, Big Tech, or Wall Street executives. You can’t go behind closed doors, take their money and then expect them to enforce the rules. #DemDebate

text: I’m not willing to give up and let a handful of monopolies dominate our economy and our democracy. You get to be the umpire in the baseball game or you get to be a team—but you can’t be both. It’s time to #BreakUpBigTech. #DemDebatehttps://elizabethwarren.com/plans/break-up-big-tech …

text: My #WealthTax says: When you make it big, pitch in two cents so that everyone else can make it too. Regardless of party affiliation, our country is working better for the rich and powerful, and worse for everyone else. We need to make our economy work for everyone. #DemDebate

text:
37 million Americans didn’t fill a prescription because of costs. 
36 million skipped a recommended test or treatment because of costs. 
40 million didn’t go to a doctor to check out a health problem because of costs.
This should never happen. It's time for #MedicareForAll.
